OL,3,CBeach deaths: Police say three women
OL,4,Crecovered from sea have been identified
OL,6,FPolice say they have identified three
OL,7,Fwomen who drowned in the sea off the
OL,8,FBrighton coast.
OL,10,FEmergency services and the coastguard
OL,11,Fwere called to Madeira Drive near
OL,12,FBrighton seafront in the early hours
OL,13,Fof Wednesday morning.
OL,15,FThe bodies of the three women were
OL,16,Frecovered from the water.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
