OL,3,CBeach deaths: Police say three women
OL,4,Crecovered from sea have been identified
OL,6,FOn Thursday, officers confirmed they
OL,7,Fhave been identified and their next of
OL,8,Fkin has been informed, but that formal
OL,9,Fidentification procedures are now
OL,10,Fbeing undertaken.
OL,12,FChief Superintendent Adam Hays said:
OL,13,F"This is an utterly heartbreaking
OL,14,Ftragedy, and my thoughts are with the
OL,15,Floved ones of these three young women
OL,16,Fafter their devastating loss.
OL,18,F"They will remain at the forefront of
OL,19,Four minds as we search for the answers
OL,20,Ftheir families, and the wider public,
OL,21,Fdesperately seek.
OL,26,@uD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
