PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1778782268
OL,3,CBeach deaths: Police say three women
OL,4,Crecovered from sea have been identified
OL,6,F"This is a sensitive investigation
OL,7,Fthat includes a number of hypotheses,
OL,8,Fand it would not be appropriate to
OL,9,Fspeculate as we to continue to gather
OL,10,Fevidence.
OL,12,F"I would once again ask for the
OL,13,Fpublic's patience while we establish
OL,14,Fthe full facts, which will be shared
OL,15,Fpublicly as soon as we are able.
OL,17,F"Anyone with information that could
OL,18,Fhelp is asked to contact police online
OL,19,For via 101, quoting Operation Ledmore."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU{D@gO]
