OL,3,CBeach deaths: Police say three women
OL,4,Crecovered from sea have been identified
OL,6,FMeanwhile Brighton Surf Life Saving
OL,7,FClub released a tribute to the three
OL,8,Fwomen.
OL,10,FPosting on X, a spokesperson said:
OL,11,F"Considering today's tragic events,
OL,12,FBrighton Surf Lifesaving Club wishes
OL,13,Fto express our deepest condolences to
OL,14,Fthe family and friends of the three
OL,15,Fyoung ladies who tragically lost their
OL,16,Flives in the sea at Brighton earlier
OL,17,Ftoday.
OL,19,F"Our thoughts are with their loved
OL,20,Fones during this incredibly difficult
OL,21,Ftime.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
