PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1778782268
OL,3,CBeach deaths: Police say three women
OL,4,Crecovered from sea have been identified
OL,6,F"We also extend our sincere gratitude
OL,7,Fand support to all rescue and
OL,8,Femergency services personnel involved
OL,9,Fin responding to this heartbreaking
OL,10,Ftragedy.
OL,12,F"Alongside the wider Brighton
OL,13,Fcommunity, we stand united in mourning
OL,14,Fthis devastating loss of life."
